<plot>Casper the Friendly Ghost doesn't like to haunt and wishes he could be in Mother Gooseland. He gets his wish and frightens the spider away from Little Miss Muffet. He them comes upon the old lady in the shoe but frightens her away, also. He is depressed, but when he rescues Red Riding Hood from the wold, Mother Goose rewards him by making up a rhyme about him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?411659</url></doc>
